<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="LoginAssets/css/main.css" /> 
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="RegisterAssets/css/main.css" /> 
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <title>Cadastro | Finance Tracker</title>
</head>
<body>
    <main class="login-container-v2">
        <section class="login-promo-v2">
            <div class="promo-content">
                <div class="logo-area">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21.21 15.89A10 10 0 1 1 8 2.83"/><path d="M22 12A10 10 0 0 0 12 2v10z"/></svg>
                    <h1>Finance Tracker</h1>
                </div>
                <p>O controle total das suas finanças. De forma simples e visual.</p>
            </div>
             <div class="promo-bg-animation"></div>
        </section>

        <section class="login-form-area-v2">
            <div class="form-wrapper-v2">
                <h2>Crie sua conta</h2>
                <p>Rápido e fácil. Comece a organizar suas finanças hoje.</p>
                
                <div class="messages-area">
                    <% if (typeof erros !== 'undefined' && erros.length > 0) { %>
                        <% erros.forEach(err => { %>
                           <div class="alert alert-danger" role="alert"><%= err %></div>
                        <% }) %>
                    <% } %>
                    <% if (typeof success !== 'undefined' && success.length > 0) { %>
                        <% success.forEach(scs => { %>
                            <div class="alert alert-success" role="alert"><%= scs %></div>
                        <% }) %>
                    <% } %>
                </div>

                <form class="login-form-real" action="/createAccount" method="POST">
                    <div class="input-group">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"></circle><path d="M5.5 21v-2a4 4 0 0 1 4-4h5a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v2"></path></svg>
                        <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required placeholder="Nome completo">
                    </div>

                    <div class="input-group">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"></path><polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"></polyline></svg>
                        <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required placeholder="Seu melhor e-mail">
                    </div>

                    <div class="input-group">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"></path></svg>
                        <input type="password" id="password" name="password" required placeholder="Crie uma senha">
                    </div>

                    <div class="input-group">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"></path></svg>
                        <input type="password" id="confirmedPassword" name="confirmedPassword" required placeholder="Confirme sua senha">
                    </div>

                    <button class="btn-submit-login" type="submit">Criar Conta</button>
                </form>

                <div class="create-account-link">
                    Já tem uma conta? <a href="/">Faça o login</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</body>
</html>